node.text:
Volunteers young and old offering time, respect, and gratitude ❤️🇺🇸 Families and friends of @militaryfamilyorg washed The Wall today. All washings are coordinated by @nationalmallnps . We are lucky to have a host of individuals and organizations that care about and for the Vietnam Veterans Memorial.
(Photos 1-7) 📸: Jenn Elisabeth Photography
(Photos 8-10) 📸: @teganluceille .
.
#care #preservation #TheWall #honorthefallen #rememberthefallen #VietnamVeteransMemorial #honor #remember #thanks #gratitude #morning #volunteer
Thank you to all that helped!! 🇺🇸😍❤️💯
Thanks to these young ones for showing kindness and respect🇺🇸👍👏
Oh my God! What a powerful picture! Let the news publish our patriotic kids be shown doing what America should be doing in their hearts🇺🇸🎈👍🏼🇵🇷❤️
And we all thank you. God bless. ❤️✝️🙏🏻🇺🇸
Thank you !! My brother's name is on that Wall Lt. Francis M. Driscoll killed on his very last mission.
